column1: Observed Geomagnetic Storm Parameters:Max Kp: 4.0 CME Note: CME start time is not completely accurate since it is a very faint partial halo. It was changed from 2017-03-20T06:00Z to 2017-03-19T18:24Z. The shock arrival is not clear since CME may have been combined and picked up by the HSS that arrived at Earth on 2017-03-21T00:00Z.
